OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS veteran refuses to pay  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffine over pro-Hamas sign   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A US military veteran has refused to   
OL,6, pay a fine for carrying a pro-Hamas    
OL,7, sign at a protest in South Yorkshire.  
OL,9,FMichael Rabb, 73, of Boulder, Colorado,
OL,10,Fwas arrested at the demonstration at   
OL,11,FSheffield City Hall on 21 October.     
OL,13,FA trial at City of London Magistrates' 
OL,14,FCourt found him guilty of displaying   
OL,15,Fthe sign in such a way as to arouse    
OL,16,Freasonable suspicion he was a member or
OL,17,Fsupporter of a proscribed organisation.
OL,19,FBut on Tuesday, he told the judge he   
OL,20,Fwas "not going to pay" the #1,000 fine.
